50
00:03:21,554 --> 00:03:22,554
Aku mengerti.

51
00:03:23,394 --> 00:03:24,494
Patut dicatat.

52
00:03:26,163 --> 00:03:29,163
Aku akan mmengembalikan perkataanku tentang kritikan.

53
00:03:29,994 --> 00:03:31,403
