70
00:04:37,664 --> 00:04:39,763
Realisasi masyarakat adil.

71
00:04:45,544 --> 00:04:47,804
Kedengarannya lucu ya? Kau pikir itu lucu?

72
00:04:48,643 --> 00:04:50,713
- Tidak.
- Kau menertawakanku.

73
00:04:51,513 --> 00:04:53,184
