74
00:04:53,443 --> 00:04:54,554
Aku bilang tidak.

75
00:04:55,354 --> 00:04:56,383
Tunggu dan lihat.

76
00:04:57,813 --> 00:04:59,724
Tunggu dan lihatlah...

77
00:05:00,523 --> 00:05:01,753
